title: David Gilmour 2016-03-25 Hollywood Bowl FLAC
description:
Here is the second night. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

David Gilmour
2016-03-25
The Hollywood Bowl
Hollywood, California USA 

Recorded & Transfered By: Robert Mullen (lvrwm) 

Equipment/Lineage: Audience/SP-CMC-25 mics (Croakies)>SP-SPSB-11(Battery 
Boost Box, with bass-roll-off at 69Hz)>Sony PCM-M10>CD Wave Editor(tracking)>
Traders Little Helper flac level 8. 

Recorder Settings: PCM-M10 at 44.1 kHz/16 bit, low mic sensitivity, manual 
record, limiter on, mic power off, low cut filter off, speed control off. 

Comments: Here is our capture of David Gilmour's 2nd night at the Hollywood Bowl. 
We were located near the center of the bowl in G2, row 20, in line with the stage
left loudspeakers. The LA Area Crowd was actually not too badly behaved this 
evening, one group of late-arrivers mid-way thru the 3rd song are briefly audible. 
The recording came out well. David and his band performed an entertaining show 
with varied material from early Pink Floyd thru his new solo material. We
enjoyed this performance. Enjoy!
